"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n答案點解一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為當width-&gt;0, 兩邊height 就會一樣<br />\nwhich is rectangle <br />\nrectangle is a special case of parallelogram</blockquote><br />\n但trapezoid唔係parallelogram"},{"pid":"5c49cd4bcee29774fef923a59eb6e502b1e83b0b","tid":451993,"uid":37489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>take完limit之後，梯形同長方形照計應該一樣答案<br />\n但梯形係咪converge快啲，方便電腦計approximation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以睇呢d方法係做緊taylor expansion既approximation<br />\n<br />\n長方形=得constant term既taylor expansion<br />\n梯形=有埋x term<br />\nSimpson's rule=有埋x^2 term<br />\n<br />\n咁in theory, consider得愈多個term就同theory最接近 eg 長方形error=O(delta x)<br />\n梯形error=O(delta x^2)<br />\nSimpson's error=O(delta x^3)"},{"pid":"c5a28c767e47d9455e5ffd113a506c6737d96b61","tid":451993,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"即係點？ 劏開個curve 人手計其實應該乜curve 都得"}]}